# Kalshi-Gopher

A Go-based API connector for [Kalshi](https://kalshi.com), the first regulated prediction market exchange in the US.

## Overview

Kalshi-Gopher provides a simple and efficient interface to interact with the Kalshi API, enabling:

- **Statistical Arbitrage** - Identify and exploit pricing inefficiencies across related markets
- **Market Data Analysis** - Fetch real-time and historical market data
- **Automated Trading** - Build and deploy trading strategies programmatically
- **Portfolio Management** - Track positions and manage risk

## Features

- Full Kalshi API coverage
- Real-time market data streaming
- Order execution and management
- Account and portfolio tracking
- Rate limiting and error handling

